Class Stub

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.Stub
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BankStub, BookStub, CartStub, ObjectStoreStub, StoreStub, TransactionsManagerStub

    public abstract class Stub
extends java.lang.Object
    Stub encapsulates network behaviour for a stub of a remote object.

    Stubs get hold of ThreadContext to execute callbacks over a Client on a Transport.
